{"tid":1037570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Lady Gaga 因曾見達賴喇嘛，遭中共封殺，奧斯卡頒獎慘被打格！","createTime":"2019-02-26T04:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T03:44:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":579,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"81479852a2b06728f59dde461a12b4fdfb9d6531","tid":1037570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=504045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D504045&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=c887471a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D504045&h=e7b3a937\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=504045</a><br />\n<br />\n第 91 屆奧斯卡頒獎典禮昨（25）日順利落幕，首度挑大樑跨足大螢幕的女神（Lady Gaga）以電影《一個巨星的誕生》獲得「最佳電影歌曲」獎，爽奪首座小金人，上台領獎時難掩內心激動當場落淚。不過卻傳出因她曾和西藏精神領袖達賴喇嘛會談遭中國封殺，昨日奧斯卡直播中，GaGa 的臉竟然全程遭到馬賽克處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/26/1799051-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F26%2F1799051-XXL.jpg&h=74fdcac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女神 GaGa 向來關心人道議題，2016年她和達賴喇嘛同時參加第84屆美國市長會議，並針對「如何面對不公義的世界」展開探討，更在個人臉書直播全程對談，會議結束後她還在所有個人社群網站上曬出和達賴喇嘛的合照，怎料此舉卻惹怒了中國網友，不僅痛批再也不支持她，官方也下令全面封殺女神 GaGa，網路媒體禁止上載其作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2016/06/28/571841-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F06%2F28%2F571841-XXL.jpg&h=9b518fbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92761d0cee30cbfe4ce0110ccea95a6a5b9feb06","tid":1037570,"uid":132462,"like":281,"dislike":1,"score":280,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"終国<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146f94598b4cb3380d1b89fdf68ccc0582e3ae1f","tid":1037570,"uid":224510,"like":354,"dislike":3,"score":351,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:34:03.000Z","msg":"好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcaa3bca47a4e90697fc5cf4a0007c518dd6416","tid":1037570,"uid":1886,"like":224,"dislike":3,"score":221,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"疑似就是因為女神 Lady Gaga 會達賴喇嘛一事，至今仍在中國的黑名單中，因此昨日中國轉播奧斯卡頒獎典禮，竟將她的整張臉全程上馬賽克，引發網友熱烈討論，狂酸：「報告長官！完全沒有畫面」、「只因 gaga 愛台灣，公開挺台灣嗎？」、「太不專業了吧！下面名字也要遮啊～封殺只封半套」。"},{"pid":"91bc39d7c28b5de2d2ffd7a5169b2247f5810ad8","tid":1037570,"uid":141151,"like":260,"dislike":1,"score":259,"quote":{"pid":"1dcaa3bca47a4e90697fc5cf4a0007c518dd6416","tid":1037570,"uid":1886,"like":224,"dislike":3,"score":221,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"疑似就是因為女神 Lady Gaga 會達賴喇嘛一事，至今仍在中國的黑名單中，因此昨日中國轉播奧斯卡頒獎典禮，竟將她的整張臉全程上馬賽克，引發網友熱烈討論，狂酸：「報告長官！完全沒有畫面」、「只因 gaga 愛台灣，公開挺台灣嗎？」、「太不專業了吧！下面名字也要遮啊～封殺只封半套」。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「太不專業了吧！下面名字也要遮啊～封殺只封半套」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ae9d43ad3ac03135a3cc2ec8d259ff93cf975c","tid":1037570,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"key 第二條奶共女個頭落去嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a58cbff10210559a48e3d28842e584704f3a4fd","tid":1037570,"uid":220701,"like":66,"dislike":10,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:36:44.000Z","msg":"女權撚做嘢未"},{"pid":"edf7173ac866a5b5c687ec0fd98465edaf8b9175","tid":1037570,"uid":24443,"like":45,"dislike":8,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:37:56.000Z","msg":"大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有夠智障"},{"pid":"60d37eef28a226b2eb7d31da66ecd62d82258cc5","tid":1037570,"uid":45368,"like":74,"dislike":3,"score":71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:51:47.000Z","msg":"我上百度睇仲有勁多資料喎<br />\n係咪fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" cla